Package ahlers.phantom.embedded

Core API.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IPhantomCommandFormatter
    Given extracted files and a Phantom process configuration, generate a complete command for invocation by PhantomProcess (AbstractProcess by extension).
    IPhantomProcess
    Describes features presented by the native Phantom process.
    IPhantomProcessConfig
    Provides command line arguments for the Phantom process itself.
    IPhantomScript
    Complements IPhantomProcessConfig in providing arguments to the command line interface, but only the portion dealing with external scripts.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PhantomDownloadConfigBuilder
    Standard IDownloadConfig factory.
    PhantomExecutable
    Represents a ready-for-execution setup, created by PhantomStarter and produces PhantomProcess.
    PhantomExtractedArtifactStoreBuilder
    Defines where and how files used at runtime are extracted from downloaded archives.
    PhantomProcess
    Represents a running instance of PhantomJS, created by PhantomExecutable.
    PhantomProcessConfigBuilder
    Standard IPhantomProcessConfig factory.
    PhantomProcessOutputConfig
    Pre-configured ProcessOutput instances.
    PhantomRuntimeConfigBuilder
    Standard IRuntimeConfig factory.
    PhantomScriptBuilder
    Standard IPhantomScript factory.
    PhantomStarter  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PhantomCommandFormatter
    Standard command factory.
    PhantomPackageResolver
    Translates components of Distribution into literal components of PhantomJS's distributed files.
    PhantomVersion
    Defines supported PhantomJS versions.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    UnsupportedArchiveException
    Declares an ArchiveType is not supported by this library.
    UnsupportedBitsizeException
    Declares an BitSize is not supported by this library.
    UnsupportedPlatformException
    Declares an Platform is not supported by this library.
